sentences: Driven by his passion for songwriting Pedro's solo recording debut came in 2008 with the Portuguese single "A beira da estrada".
Recorded in 2009, it has generated Pedro's biggest success to date.
The Light reached a peek position of 11th on 5 May 2009 (see Charts).
In 2010 "Fooled Again?" was discovered by CBC radio producer Amanda Putz and featured on CBC Radio 1 show Bandwidth.
The track also made the CBC radio 3 track of the day.
After several other singles releases and collaborative efforts his first full-length album "Discovery" was released March 2011.
In 2017 the critically acclaimed Netflix show 13 Reason Why used Pedro's song "Finding My Wings" on the show's soundtrack.
